Ratings of relational satisfaction and commitment from 282 (Q)ueer couples

Source: R/commitmentQ-data.R
commitmentQ.Rd

A data set containing 5 ratings of satisfaction and 5 ratings of commitment for each member of a same-sex romantic dyad. Measured using the Investment Model Scale subscales (Rubult, Martz, & Agnew, 1998). Data are from analyses under review (Sakaluk, Fisher, and Kilshaw). Variable names follow a stem-partner-item ("spi") order, with a delimiter (".") between the stem and distinguishing partner character, and another delimiter ("_") between the distinguishing partner character and item number.

data(commitmentQ)
